OL,3,CSheep dog hit by car is back at work
OL,4,Cafter having face rebuilt
OL,6,FBorder Collie Pearl is back home with
OL,7,Fher owner Lucy Ballard at Wadebridge,
OL,8,FCornwall after having her jaw rebuilt
OL,9,Ffollowing an accident in which she was
OL,10,Fhit by a car.
OL,12,FJust eight weeks after the hit and run
OL,13,Fcrash Pearl, who is a working
OL,14,Fsheepdog, has returned to the fields.
OL,16,FPearl was treated at Cave Veterinary
OL,17,FSpecialists, in West Buckland,
OL,18,FSomerset, after the crash where she
OL,19,Fsuffered injuries to her face and
OL,20,Fmultiple fractures of her jaw.
