OL,3,CSheep dog hit by car is back at work
OL,4,Cafter having face rebuilt
OL,6,FSpecialist vet Annabel McFadzean
OL,7,Fsaid:"The upper part of her jaw was
OL,8,Fbasically detached from her face. She
OL,9,Fhad bone, dental and soft tissue
OL,10,Fdamage which all needed to be urgently
OL,11,Faddressed.
OL,13,F"Her soft tissue injuries were so
OL,14,Fextensive over the upper jaw that
OL,15,Fthere was concern whether it would
OL,16,Fsurvive.
OL,18,F"We were also concerned that Pearl
OL,19,Fwould require multiple procedures to
OL,20,Fenable her to fully recover."
