OL,3,CSheep dog hit by car is back at work
OL,4,Cafter having face rebuilt
OL,6,FA CT scan of Pearl's head and a
OL,7,Fdetailed oral examination were carried
OL,8,Fout to accurately access the full
OL,9,Fextent of the severe trauma she had
OL,10,Fsuffered and help plan for the
OL,11,Fchallenging surgery she required.
OL,13,FMs McFadzean added: "First of all
OL,14,FPearl needed multiple dental
OL,15,Fextractions with all her upper incisor
OL,16,Fteeth removed as they had undergone
OL,17,Froot fracture injuries.
OL,26,@uD@UOU
