OL,3,CSheep dog hit by car is back at work
OL,4,Cafter having face rebuilt
OL,6,F"We were able to save both her injured
OL,7,Fcanine teeth, though, by performing
OL,8,Froot canal treatments on them as they
OL,9,Fhad lost their blood supply in the
OL,10,Ftrauma.
OL,12,F"The detailed dental work was then
OL,13,Ffollowed by the application of an
OL,14,Fintraoral wire and splint to repair
OL,15,Fher upper jaw and restore it into its
OL,16,Fnormal position. Finally, the
OL,17,Fwidespread soft tissue damage was
OL,18,Frepaired.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
