OL,3,CSheep dog hit by car is back at work
OL,4,Cafter having face rebuilt
OL,6,F"Everything went well, and Pearl
OL,7,Frecovered positively from the
OL,8,Foperation and was soon allowed home
OL,9,Funder strict orders for complete rest
OL,10,Ffor two months.
OL,12,F"She then returned to us to have the
OL,13,Fsplint in her jaw removed as the bones
OL,14,Fhad now healed.
OL,16,F"Miraculously, the soft tissue had
OL,17,Falso healed without complications and
OL,18,Fshe was able to return to work soon
OL,19,Fafterwards.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
