OL,6,F"Pearl's recovery has been truly
OL,7,Fremarkable. I'm delighted, not just
OL,8,Fthat she can function again but that
OL,9,Fshe's been able to get back to work
OL,10,Fherding the sheep!"
OL,12,FWhen she Pearl off to herd sheep for
OL,13,Fthe first time after the crash owner
OL,14,FLucy Ballard just shouted "8 weeks
OL,15,FI've waited for this."
